</SP>
<P>The Court, con&s;idering that the pri&s;oner &s;tood mute from ob&s;tinacy, or|dered the plea of NOT GUILTY to be entered for him on the record; which the Clerk did accordingly, and the Attorney General thereupon joined i&s;&s;ue.</P>
