<P>Then the jury who were returned on the pannel, were all called over, and the appearances of all tho&s;e that an&s;wered to the call, were recorded, 72 jurors appeared. Note: 80 jurors were &s;ummoned and returned, under the authority of the 4th. &s;ection of the ballotting act of 1785.</P>
